| `src/overlay/panelUtils.ts` | `getIndicatorType` now accepts optional `activeState` param; checks state-keyed dirty props first, returning `"state"` for green. Updated `getIndicatorTitle` for state type. |
| `src/overlay/WebflowPanel.tsx` | `ind()` callback now passes `activeState` to `getIndicatorType`. `sectionInd()` prioritizes `"state"` over `"modified"`. |
| `src/overlay/__tests__/panelUtils.test.ts` | 7 new tests covering state indicator detection, priority over base-state, and color/title output |

